- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the impact of social media on e-commerce and customer engagement. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is also a possible category as the paper may involve analyzing social behavior and communication patterns on Twitter.
